{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3539,"text":"You know, we wake up in the morning,"},{"time":6615,"text":"you get dressed, put on your shoes,"},{"time":9135,"text":"you head out into the world."},{"time":11647,"text":"You plan on coming back, getting undressed,"},{"time":15898,"text":"going to bed,"},{"time":18123,"text":"waking up, doing it again,"},{"time":19877,"text":"and that anticipation, that rhythm,"},{"time":23025,"text":"helps give us a structure"},{"time":25295,"text":"to how we organize ourselves and our lives,"},{"time":28883,"text":"and gives it a measure of predictability."},{"time":32363,"text":"Living in New York City, as I do,"},{"time":34751,"text":"it's almost as if, with so many people doing so many things"},{"time":41990,"text":"at the same time in such close quarters,"},{"time":45340,"text":"it's almost like life is dealing you extra hands"},{"time":48579,"text":"out of that deck."},{"time":50105,"text":"You're never, there's just, juxtapositions are possible"},{"time":54773,"text":"that just aren't, you don't think they're going to happen."},{"time":59776,"text":"And you never think you're going to be the guy"},{"time":62119,"text":"who's walking down the street"},{"time":63749,"text":"and, because you choose to go down one side or the other,"},{"time":67171,"text":"the rest of your life is changed forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70331,"text":"And one night, I'm riding the uptown local train."},{"time":76059,"text":"I get on. I tend to be a little bit vigilant"},{"time":79555,"text":"when I get on the subway."},{"time":81672,"text":"I'm not one of the people zoning out with headphones"},{"time":84718,"text":"or a book."},{"time":86101,"text":"And I get on the car, and I look, and I"},{"time":88907,"text":"notice this couple,"},{"time":91491,"text":"college-aged, student-looking kids,"},{"time":94979,"text":"a guy and a girl, and they're sitting next to each other,"},{"time":96776,"text":"and she's got her leg draped over his knee,"},{"time":99425,"text":"and they're doing -- they have this little contraption,"},{"time":103585,"text":"and they're tying these knots,"},{"time":105343,"text":"and they're doing it with one hand,"},{"time":107180,"text":"they're doing it left-handed and right-handed very quickly,"},{"time":111144,"text":"and then she'll hand the thing to him and he'll do it."},{"time":113392,"text":"I've never seen anything like this."},{"time":114593,"text":"It's almost like they're practicing magic tricks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117977,"text":"And at the next stop, a guy gets on the car,"},{"time":122296,"text":"and he has this sort of visiting professor look to him."},{"time":126274,"text":"He's got the overstuffed leather satchel"},{"time":128394,"text":"and the rectangular file case and a laptop bag"},{"time":131704,"text":"and the tweed jacket with the leather patches,"},{"time":134216,"text":"and — (Laughter) —"},{"time":136193,"text":"he looks at them, and then"},{"time":139016,"text":"in a blink of an eye, he kneels down in front of them,"},{"time":142032,"text":"and he starts to say,"},{"time":143697,"text":"\"You know, listen, here's how you can do it. Look,"},{"time":145766,"text":"if you do this -- \" and he takes the laces out of their hand,"},{"time":148385,"text":"and instantly, he starts tying these knots,"},{"time":151696,"text":"and even better than they were doing it, remarkably."},{"time":156357,"text":"And it turns out they are medical students"},{"time":159437,"text":"on their way to a lecture about the latest"},{"time":161549,"text":"suturing techniques, and he's the guy giving the lecture."},{"time":164775,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166383,"text":"So he starts to tell them, and he's like,"},{"time":168797,"text":"\"No, this is very important here. You know,"},{"time":171305,"text":"when you're needing these knots,"},{"time":173585,"text":"it's going to be, you know, everything's"},{"time":175177,"text":"going to be happening at the same time, it's going to be --"},{"time":178930,"text":"you're going to have all this information coming at you,"},{"time":182567,"text":"there's going to be organs getting in the way,"},{"time":184063,"text":"it's going to be slippery,"},{"time":186098,"text":"and"},{"time":187408,"text":"it's just very important that you be able to do these"},{"time":190166,"text":"beyond second nature, each hand, left hand, right hand,"},{"time":193536,"text":"you have to be able to do them without seeing your fingers.\""},{"time":196364,"text":"And at that moment, when I heard that,"},{"time":198734,"text":"I just got catapulted out of the subway car into a night"},{"time":205806,"text":"when I had been getting a ride in an ambulance"},{"time":208940,"text":"from the sidewalk where I had been stabbed"},{"time":213431,"text":"to the trauma room of St. Vincent's Hospital in Manhattan,"},{"time":217750,"text":"and what had happened was"},{"time":219739,"text":"a gang had come in from Brooklyn."},{"time":222948,"text":"As part of an initiation for three of their members,"},{"time":225571,"text":"they had to kill somebody,"},{"time":227275,"text":"and I happened to be the guy walking down Bleecker Street"},{"time":230662,"text":"that night,"},{"time":231959,"text":"and they jumped on me without a word."},{"time":236396,"text":"One of the very lucky things,"},{"time":238721,"text":"when I was at Notre Dame, I was on the boxing team,"},{"time":241729,"text":"so I put my hands up right away, instinctively."},{"time":246377,"text":"The guy on the right had a knife with a 10-inch blade,"},{"time":249929,"text":"and he went in under my elbow,"},{"time":253222,"text":"and it went up and cut my inferior vena cava."},{"time":257689,"text":"If you know anything about anatomy,"},{"time":259409,"text":"that's not a good thing to get cut,"},{"time":261117,"text":"and everything, of course, on the way up,"},{"time":264275,"text":"and then — I still had my hands up —"},{"time":266165,"text":"he pulled it out and went for my neck,"},{"time":268654,"text":"and sunk it in up to the hilt in my neck,"},{"time":272859,"text":"and I got one straight right punch"},{"time":275583,"text":"and knocked the middle guy out."},{"time":277354,"text":"The other guy was still working on me,"},{"time":279567,"text":"collapsing my other lung,"},{"time":281432,"text":"and I managed to, by hitting that guy, to get a minute."},{"time":287412,"text":"I ran down the street and collapsed,"},{"time":289505,"text":"and the ambulance guys intubated me on the sidewalk"},{"time":292552,"text":"and let the trauma room know"},{"time":295025,"text":"they had an incoming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296643,"text":"And one of the"},{"time":299642,"text":"side effects of having major massive blood loss"},{"time":303583,"text":"is you get tunnel vision,"},{"time":305430,"text":"so I remember being on the stretcher"},{"time":307243,"text":"and having a little nickel-sized cone of vision,"},{"time":311248,"text":"and I was moving my head around"},{"time":312797,"text":"and we got to St. Vincent's,"},{"time":314153,"text":"and we're racing down this hallway,"},{"time":315796,"text":"and I see the lights going,"},{"time":318064,"text":"and it's a peculiar effect of memories like that."},{"time":324792,"text":"They don't really go to the usual place that memories go."},{"time":328971,"text":"They kind of have this vault where they're stored in high-def,"},{"time":334175,"text":"and George Lucas did all the sound effects. (Laughter)"},{"time":338660,"text":"So sometimes, remembering them, it's like,"},{"time":343156,"text":"it's not like any other kind of memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346880,"text":"And I get into the trauma room,"},{"time":349552,"text":"and they're waiting for me, and the lights are there,"},{"time":352574,"text":"and I'd been able to breathe a little more now,"},{"time":357869,"text":"because the blood has left, had been filling up my lungs"},{"time":361348,"text":"and I was having a very hard time breathing,"},{"time":363314,"text":"but now it's kind of gone into the stretcher."},{"time":366356,"text":"And I said, \"Is there anything I can do to help?\""},{"time":369660,"text":"and — (Laughter) —"},{"time":371432,"text":"the nurse kind of had a hysterical laugh, and"},{"time":374746,"text":"I'm turning my head trying to see everybody,"},{"time":376994,"text":"and I had this weird memory of being in college"},{"time":380810,"text":"and raising,"},{"time":383722,"text":"raising money for the flood victims of Bangladesh,"},{"time":387779,"text":"and then I look over and my anesthesiologist"},{"time":390236,"text":"is clamping the mask on me, and I think,"},{"time":391769,"text":"\"He looks Bangladeshi,\" — (Laughter) —"},{"time":393830,"text":"and I just have those two facts, and I just think,"},{"time":397315,"text":"\"This could work somehow.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":401029,"text":"And then I go out, and"},{"time":403307,"text":"they work on me for the rest of the night,"},{"time":405083,"text":"and I needed about 40 units of blood to keep me there"},{"time":410096,"text":"while they did their work,"},{"time":413141,"text":"and the surgeon took out about a third of my intestines,"},{"time":417365,"text":"my cecum, organs I didn't know that I had,"},{"time":420784,"text":"and he later told me one of the last things he did"},{"time":423155,"text":"while he was in there was to remove my appendix for me,"},{"time":426500,"text":"which I thought was great, you know,"},{"time":428723,"text":"just a little tidy thing there at the end. (Laughter)"},{"time":431886,"text":"And I came to in the morning."},{"time":436204,"text":"Out of anesthetic, he had let them know"},{"time":438020,"text":"that he wanted to be there, and he had given me"},{"time":441508,"text":"about a two percent chance of living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444703,"text":"So he was there when I woke up,"},{"time":446615,"text":"and it was, waking up was like"},{"time":448776,"text":"breaking through the ice into a frozen lake of pain."},{"time":454993,"text":"It was that enveloping,"},{"time":457096,"text":"and there was only one spot that didn't hurt"},{"time":461268,"text":"worse than anything I'd ever felt,"},{"time":462741,"text":"and it was my instep,"},{"time":464147,"text":"and he was holding the arch of my foot"},{"time":467893,"text":"and rubbing the instep with his thumb."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471761,"text":"And I looked up, and he's like,"},{"time":474697,"text":"\"Good to see you,\""},{"time":475818,"text":"and I was trying to remember what had happened"},{"time":479754,"text":"and trying to get my head around everything,"},{"time":481472,"text":"and the pain was just overwhelming, and he said,"},{"time":485529,"text":"\"You know, we didn't cut your hair. I thought"},{"time":488905,"text":"you might have gotten strength from your hair like Samson,"},{"time":493277,"text":"and you're going to need all the strength you can get.\""},{"time":496060,"text":"And in those days, my hair was down to my waist,"},{"time":499769,"text":"I drove a motorcycle, I was unmarried,"},{"time":502641,"text":"I owned a bar, so those were different times. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":507950,"text":"But"},{"time":510210,"text":"I had three days of life support,"},{"time":513182,"text":"and everybody was expecting,"},{"time":516963,"text":"due to just the massive amount of what they had had to do"},{"time":521456,"text":"that I wasn't going to make it,"},{"time":523284,"text":"so it was three days of"},{"time":525329,"text":"everybody was either waiting for me to die or poop,"},{"time":528156,"text":"and — (Laughter) —"},{"time":529752,"text":"when I finally pooped, then that somehow,"},{"time":532711,"text":"surgically speaking, that's like you crossed some good line,"},{"time":536118,"text":"and, um — (Laughter) —"},{"time":537158,"text":"on that day, the surgeon came in"},{"time":540423,"text":"and whipped the sheet off of me."},{"time":543615,"text":"He had three or four friends with him,"},{"time":545276,"text":"and he does that, and they all look,"},{"time":547678,"text":"and there was no infection,"},{"time":549559,"text":"and they bend over me and they're poking and prodding,"},{"time":552429,"text":"and they're like, \"There's no hematomas, blah blah,"},{"time":554526,"text":"look at the color,\" and they're talking amongst themselves"},{"time":557396,"text":"and I'm, like, this restored automobile"},{"time":560319,"text":"that he's just going, \"Yeah, I did that.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":563510,"text":"And it was just,"},{"time":566534,"text":"it was amazing, because these guys are high-fiving him"},{"time":569670,"text":"over how good I turned out, you know? (Laughter)"},{"time":571730,"text":"And it's my zipper, and I've still got the staples in"},{"time":575251,"text":"and everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576487,"text":"And"},{"time":578702,"text":"later on, when I got out"},{"time":581313,"text":"and the flashbacks and the"},{"time":586925,"text":"nightmares were giving me a hard time,"},{"time":591430,"text":"I went back to him"},{"time":593112,"text":"and I was sort of asking him,"},{"time":597005,"text":"you know, what am I gonna do?"},{"time":599186,"text":"And I think, kind of, as a surgeon, he basically said,"},{"time":603794,"text":"\"Kid, I saved your life."},{"time":605520,"text":"Like, now you can do whatever you want, like,"},{"time":608170,"text":"you gotta get on with that."},{"time":609836,"text":"It's like I gave you a new car"},{"time":611668,"text":"and you're complaining about not finding parking."},{"time":613960,"text":"Like, just, go out, and, you know, do your best."},{"time":617561,"text":"But you're alive. That's what it's about.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":622367,"text":"And then I hear, \"Bing-bong,\" and the subway doors"},{"time":628148,"text":"are closing, and my stop is next, and I look at these kids,"},{"time":634387,"text":"and I go, I think to myself,"},{"time":636256,"text":"\"I'm going to lift my shirt up"},{"time":637818,"text":"and show them,\" — (Laughter) —"},{"time":639435,"text":"and then I think, \"No, this is the New York City subway,"},{"time":641664,"text":"that's going to lead to other things.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645295,"text":"And so I just think, they got their lecture to go to."},{"time":649337,"text":"I step off, I'm standing on the platform,"},{"time":653298,"text":"and I feel my index finger"},{"time":656162,"text":"in"},{"time":658341,"text":"the first scar that I ever got,"},{"time":662044,"text":"from my umbilical cord,"},{"time":665158,"text":"and then around that, is traced"},{"time":668396,"text":"the last scar that I got"},{"time":670892,"text":"from my surgeon,"},{"time":673269,"text":"and I think that, that chance encounter"},{"time":678583,"text":"with those kids on the street with their knives"},{"time":682472,"text":"led me"},{"time":684905,"text":"to my surgical team,"},{"time":688030,"text":"and their training"},{"time":692105,"text":"and their skill"},{"time":694221,"text":"and, always, a little bit of luck"},{"time":697641,"text":"pushed back against chaos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":700612,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":704666,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":713610,"text":"Thank you. Very lucky to be here. Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}